Package main

Class FoodItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.FoodItem
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Biscuit, Pizza, Ramen, Ration, Salad, SpaceFruit
    public class FoodItem
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements the generic superclass of a food item, which is used to reduce the hunger of crew members by consuming them
    Author:
    Jackie Qiu

      • equals

        public boolean equals​(java.lang.Object o)
